column5: This site is awesome.  I have been a member since 2007 and no fail, every single time I have had a question, I have received valuable input (and I have had a lot of questions).  There are a lot of good people on this site and I am thankful for it!
Good to hear Pete, glad the site has been helpful for you  It is definately a great place
Just don`t ask which brand of outboard is better!!!
almost time for the tiller and console thread again. Thanks for the koodos Pete it makes me realize it is not a waste of my time to help keep this board on an even keel.   Art
And wash that down with a hockey thread!!!
How about a question about left hand reels for right handed baitcasters???
